Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:09.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[NEWS ANNOUNCER (F)] It looks\Nto be a wet one tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:10.93,Main,,0,0,0,,with scattered showers\Nthroughout the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Suppose I won't\Nbe hanging anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:13.97,Main,,0,0,0,,outside to dry tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Grandma, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:18.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi, want a snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:20.73,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something\NI gotta check first!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Oh, come on!\NWhy are you so slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:27.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not used to\NAyumu's laptop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:37.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:43.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:46.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona really is trying to gather\Nall the Selectors together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:52.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It's happening\Nreally close to here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:40.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Around here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] They're only one\Nbuilding away from a Tetris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:04.22,Main,,0,0,0,,And then the whole city\Nmight just disappear on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh-uh. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:21.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.04,Main,,0,0,0,,If something's\Nbothering you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:28.00,Main,,0,0,0,,or if you've got something\Non your mind, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:30.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it... true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.51,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause people say they\Nnever know what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't what\NI was trying to say before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I meant you try to figure\Nthings out all on your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:45.02,Main,,0,0,0,,and hold everything inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhhh... You know,\Nkinda like I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:51.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Still friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Like back when we bought these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,'Course we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You're one of the kindest\Npeople I've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Hey!\NCome on, knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You're making me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Turns out you're\Nalso one of the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:08.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:12.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish...\NI could be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:19.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki... Tama... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:24.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I've decided\Nto battle Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:28.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha... What are\Nyou talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you said\Nyou gave up battling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Yeah... I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:33.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, I have\Na wish to fight for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's... a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It's to save you. You and Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Plus everyone else\Nwho became LRIGs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I swear! I'll bring\Nyou all back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:54.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get you out\Nof this crazy game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care what I\Nhave to sacrifice to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.59,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my one and only wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That's sweet, but\Nit can't be done. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause like me, every LRIG\Nused to be a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,And the LRIGs who\Nreplace winning Selectors
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:17.78,Main,,0,0,0,,become normal girls again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though\Nthey're bound by an oath
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,to fulfill your wish, there's\Na limit to what they can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,So you're telling me\Nthere are some wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.87,Main,,0,0,0,,that can never come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Like going back in time\Nor reshaping reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:33.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] But it's not\Nmy place to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:37.88,Main,,0,0,0,,which are possible\Nand which are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Most wishes can come true
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.30,Main,,0,0,0,,thanks to the\Nefforts of the LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Assuming, of course, that she\Nupholds her end of the oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Whether it's due to personal\Nmorality, common sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:53.23,Main,,0,0,0,,or simply a matter\Nself-preservation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:56.31,Main,,0,0,0,,an LRIG may become reluctant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.69,Main,,0,0,0,,But she must cast\Nthese feelings aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.99,Main,,0,0,0,,and prioritize the Selector's\Nwish above her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.53,Main,,0,0,0,,If an LRIG refuses the wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...she will remain\Ntrapped in her card,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.99,Main,,0,0,0,,unable to return\Nto the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Therefore, to\Nguarantee both the wish
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.96,Main,,0,0,0,,and her eventual\Nescape from her card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.75,Main,,0,0,0,,From the moment they meet,\Nshe must do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,and everything to\Nreach that conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Even deceiving her Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Otherwise,\Nyou wouldn't agree
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.93,Main,,0,0,0,,to the ritual of\Nacknowledgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a catalyst, you see, a\Ntrigger for the transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Now... the oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's, uh...\N"I accept."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,"The laws of the Selector."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,"I accept the laws of\Nthe Selector." And, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH] "And upon\Nthis sacred oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:49.66,Main,,0,0,0,,a new Eternal Girl\Nshall be born!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:52.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Once an Eternal Girl,\Nshe is obligated
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.54,Main,,0,0,0,,to fulfill the wish\Nthat has been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Though she may\Nhave deceived you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,she has entered a contract\Nthat cannot be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.55,Main,,0,0,0,,For if she fails\Nto uphold her end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:05.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The Eternal Girl\Nwill disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Remember\Nwhat Hanayo said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] About how you couldn't\Nwish Hitoe's memories back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.10,Main,,0,0,0,,That probably\Nmeans you can't just
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.14,Main,,0,0,0,,"undo" things with another wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:19.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but those girls,\Nthe ones who are LRIGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I have no idea\Nhow to get them out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,or if it's even possible,\Nbut, this Mayu girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The one in that\Nweird white room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,She might. I just\Ndon't know how to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,get back to that\Nplace to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can get 'em out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:37.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why,\Nbut somewhere deep down,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like I might know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I might be able to turn\Nall the LRIGs back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!\NYou really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kinda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But there's this feeling,\Nsomething inside saying
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,"Yes. I can do this thing."\NWell, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:54.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Makes me wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] No, that's crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] If the Eternal Girls\Nhave so little power,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:03.40,Main,,0,0,0,,what's the point\Nin going through
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:05.07,Main,,0,0,0,,all this mess\Nin the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We're stuck in a card,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.61,Main,,0,0,0,,and they die if they\Ncan't fulfill the wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,If we couldn't make\Nthe wish come true
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.83,Main,,0,0,0,,and they're us now, then\Naren't you condemning us all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] There are exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] That is to say,\Nsome Eternal Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.08,Main,,0,0,0,,are more... "special"\Nthan others...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You may lack\Nthe power to create
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,this fairy tale\Nending you so desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.09,Main,,0,0,0,,but there is magic\Nyet in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] You expect\Nme to buy into
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,some fantasy\Nmumbo-jumbo like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Given what you\Nhave just been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:39.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you would deny\Nthe very concept so flippantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,And now it seems\Nthe time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:52.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Morning dawns\Non your life as an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You now go to\Nmeet your Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.95,Main,,0,0,0,,No, wait! Tell me who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[glass shatters]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:11.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] I'm the one who\Nwill always be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:14.14,Main,,0,0,0,,In the rift that exists\Nbetween the world of the cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.93,Main,,0,0,0,,and the world of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Good luck. And goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:22.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You know,\NTama does seem
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.49,Main,,0,0,0,,awfully different\Nfrom other LRIGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's one of those\Nso-called "special" ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,So... maybe my\Nwish can come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] No dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:37.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember, if you\Ntake the oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:41.08,Main,,0,0,0,,you're just gonna turn\Ninto an LRIG like I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Since my wish is to release\Nall the LRIGs from their cards
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,and make them real again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,maybe that means I won't\Nbe able to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Are you nuts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.55,Main,,0,0,0,,For all you know,\Nwe could get fixed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,while you're stuck\Nas an LRIG forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:57.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Or, God forbid, something worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I know, but I--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Ruko, please, you've\Ngotta give this more thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:04.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, sure, if you're a card,\Nmaybe I could find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.61,Main,,0,0,0,,And maybe we could be\Nfriends like we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,But, people\Nwho aren't Selectors,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.82,Main,,0,0,0,,like your grandmother\Nand brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.45,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll never see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:35.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hitoe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'd like\Nmy LRIG back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hitoe, look, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I don't care,\Njust give her back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hold on,\Nw-we need to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Calm down.\NIt's cool. I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,and I have nothing\Nto say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm taking my LRIG
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:13.38,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to compete\Nin Iona's fan event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.72,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to\Ntalk to me so badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.05,Main,,0,0,0,,you can do it\Non the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:35.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] If my wish comes true,\NI might never see Grandma again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[elevator dings]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:45.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma, I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Oh. Hello.\NYes, she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] She's even made friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm, she sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.55,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no point blaming\Nyourself for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of hearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.60,Main,,0,0,0,,This has all been\Nsettled before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,And I won't\Nhave you pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,to be her mother, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:12.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't hold a\Nthing against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.82,Main,,0,0,0,,but when you said you\Nweren't meant to be a parent,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:18.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I was inclined to agree,\Nand my opinion hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember, I love\Nhaving the kids here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:23.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Ayumu and Ruko\Nare both utter joys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:25.16,Main,,0,0,0,,They always brighten my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[floorboards creak]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Right. Okay,\NI'll call you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You take care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, Ru. You about\Nready for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:37.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Was that Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:43.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I finally thought of a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:48.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Y'see, when I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad were\Nsupposed to be close
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.98,Main,,0,0,0,,but all they did was fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It made me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It made me think if you\Ngot close to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,you'd just end up getting hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,so I stayed away from people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:06.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, except for you\Nand Ayumu, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:09.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I needed\Nanyone else but you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:12.46,Main,,0,0,0,,But over the last\Nfew weeks, that's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I've actually made\Nsome true friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,and they're real\Nimportant to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,And it's because\Nof them that, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You were telling\Nme the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:26.10,Main,,0,0,0,,you hoped you could do\Nsomething for your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this wish of yours for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] It's not something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:34.15,Main,,0,0,0,,No, of course not,\NI mean--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] So it's\Nsomething good, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. I think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It kinda has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You have a\Ngood heart, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:49.16,Main,,0,0,0,,And you believe\Nyour wish is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:52.33,Main,,0,0,0,,The very fact that you wished\Nit for your friends instead of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:55.71,Main,,0,0,0,,for yourself proves to me you're\Nprobably on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.67,Main,,0,0,0,,So you do what\Nyou need to, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure it will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:03.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Your friends are very lucky\Nto have you and so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:08.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Aw, it's all right,\Nthere's no reason to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:11.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:17.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:18.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:22.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] So you're...\Ngonna battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:23.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:26.49,Main,,0,0,0,,We're gonna take on\Nthat mean girl Iona again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:27.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet you can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] No! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Grandma doesn't\Nknow what could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,If she did, she wouldn't\Nhave said all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.42,Main,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't let\Nyou risk your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I'm stuck\Nin this dumb card forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.30,Main,,0,0,0,,It's better than being alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You may never see me\Nor your Grandma again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:46.05,Main,,0,0,0,,So please don't do this, Ru,\NI don't want to lose you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,But Tama, I'm sure\Nmy plan is gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] But Yuzuki\Nsaid it might not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:55.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Then what'll happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:58.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\Nbut I've gotta do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:01.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't become an LRIG\Nand I won't let you stay one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I promise...\Nwe'll never be apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:10.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You and I will do\Neverything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:16.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Have yummy\Nbreakfasts with Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:20.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Run so we're\Nnot late to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hang out with\NYuzuki and Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:26.05,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll all be best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.47,Main,,0,0,0,,It's closed now,\Nbut during the summer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,we'll go to the candy\Nshop on the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,They've got this ice cream\Nyou wouldn't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:35.52,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll try a new\Nflavor every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Trust me. You'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.65,Main,,0,0,0,,So, sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:49.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] It does, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I'm sorry, Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:16:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I am... But...\NI have to finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU]\NBe careful now, okay, Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:08.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Think you'll be\Nhome in time for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,And do you think we could\Nhave potatoes au gratin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.31,Main,,0,0,0,,With lots of bacon\Nthe way you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Oh, please!\NLove you, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] All right. Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Oh, wow. These girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,All of 'em are Selectors here\Nto fight for their wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[TV static crackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTORS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the fan event.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:17:02.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Rather, welcome to the\NSelectors-only WIXOSS party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.48,Main,,0,0,0,,This building is\Nowned by my Father
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:06.57,Main,,0,0,0,,and the work crews\Nare off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:10.61,Main,,0,0,0,,So we don't have to worry\Nabout being disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.78,Main,,0,0,0,,We've all been battling\Nto make our wishes come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.29,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet, we don't\Nknow how many wins
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:20.41,Main,,0,0,0,,we need to make that happen.\NFrustrating, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I started to wonder:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,What if there was something\Nwe could do to change that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hence this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:29.05,Main,,0,0,0,,With so many Selectors\Ngathered to do battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.47,Main,,0,0,0,,some are bound\Nto win enough
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,to meet these\Nelusive conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,As a result, a large\Nnumber of Eternal Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.27,Main,,0,0,0,,will be born right here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:40.39,Main,,0,0,0,,These Selectors...\NThey have no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:43.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Now, obviously,\Nfor each of you who wins,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,there will be another who loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Speaking personally, I have\Nno desire to fight anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.65,Main,,0,0,0,,but the strongest\NSelectors available.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I have assigned you all\Nto tournament brackets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,If you win a battle, you\Nprogress to the next round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:01.04,Main,,0,0,0,,If you lose, you're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:04.13,Main,,0,0,0,,This will at least\Nprevent multiple losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.84,Main,,0,0,0,,And the Selector who makes\Nit all the way to the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll be\Nfacing me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:20.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Twelfth floor...\NRoom four?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:34.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Is everyone ready?\NI hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Because the\Nbattle begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:38.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTORS] Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:49.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, Grow!\NGothic Boundary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR C screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I know it hurts,\Nbut when I'm finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,none of you will ever have\Nto go through this again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:19:01.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon: Mitsurugi!\NThis is the final blow, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:08.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[LRIG screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:14.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Please, I need\Nyou to agree to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Otherwise my wish\Nwon't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I'm sorry, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,But we have to do it my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:29.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] We have to keep battling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I shoulda\Nseen this coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess so. You ready\Nto talk to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Like I said:\Non the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH] Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.41,Main,,0,0,0,,No new Eternal Girls\Nhave been born yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:02.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Not that I sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,\Nit looks like some Selectors
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,are losing their third\Nand final battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I will find my way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:22.85,Main,,0,0,0,,To that white room\Nwhere she's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Bounce Sevieria,\Nand attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:25.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:27.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki! Grow now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:32.40,Main,,0,0,0,,And banish Mikagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Dang it. She's so much\Nbetter than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Splitting Conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Tama! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Yuzuki, attack!\NBanish Square!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:53.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,It's wrong...\NIt's all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you\Nmean, "wrong"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] It's not supposed\Nto be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:02.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Why can't you\Nremember how it was
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.97,Main,,0,0,0,,when we played before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] We used to play\Nfor fun, not to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:12.61,Main,,0,0,0,,No LRIGs, no battles, no wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:15.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Back then, I thought\Nthat wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted serious battles--\Nserious victories,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.90,Main,,0,0,0,,instead of just\Nappreciating what I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:21.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Now it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:28.25,Main,,0,0,0,,We can never just enjoy\Nplaying games again, as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,And I hate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:36.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it.\NNow she's sad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,That means she must remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,She still has memories of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:41.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:46.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Like Ruko said,\Nwe all used to be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:47.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:48.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:50.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Did that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I need\Nyou to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Knock it off,\NYuzuki, you're hurting her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:22:00.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I know, but do you\Nwant her to stay like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Her life being controlled\Nby these stupid battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:07.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't. I want to be\Nbest friends like we were!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:10.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Me too! I don't\Nwanna battle like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:13.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna do it as friends,\Nlike we used to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It was so much fun,\Nplease remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.63,Main,,0,0,0,,No, please stop it,\Nthis is killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:19.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe! Remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:22.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wish to make\Nfriends already came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:25.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You can quit all of this!\NYou still have us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:27.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it...\NStop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.06,0:22:31.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] You can do this, Hitoe!\NJust remember how we used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you please\Njust shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:33.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.89,0:22:35.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I don't want\Nto hear any more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:38.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I just want to make my\Nwish come true, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:41.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Aren't you listening?!\NI told you it already did! So...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:42.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:43.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:46.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] No, okay?\NThis wasn't part of the deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:48.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You promised\Nwe would battle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,and you'd grant me a wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha-- I--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.71,0:22:57.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Her scrunchie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:22:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,She still has it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Now, then.\NReady to say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:09.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I've waited\Nlong enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:13.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Soon I will face my\Nfinal battle as Iona Urazoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:14.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Oh, one final note.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:16.73,Main,,0,0,0,,While it's been a\Nblast giving beatdowns
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:18.90,Main,,0,0,0,,to other Selectors with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna miss you\None bit, you rotten bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:30.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Still, I'll be beside\Nyou to the very end... Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time:\N"That Choice..."
